# Arden AI Mental Health Companion - Environment Configuration
#
# SECURITY NOTE: This file is for FRONTEND environment variables only.
# All API keys (Gemini, LiveKit, Overshoot) must be stored in Supabase Secrets.
# See SETUP.md for instructions on setting Supabase secrets.

# ============================================================================
# SUPABASE CONFIGURATION (Public Keys - Safe for Frontend)
# ============================================================================
# Get these from your Supabase project settings:
# https://app.supabase.com/project/YOUR_PROJECT/settings/api

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: DO NOT PUT API KEYS HERE
# ============================================================================
#
# The following API keys MUST be set as Supabase Secrets (NOT in this file):
# - GEMINI_API_KEY          (for AI sentiment analysis)
# - LIVEKIT_API_KEY         (for real-time voice)
# - LIVEKIT_API_SECRET      (for real-time voice)
# - OVERSHOOT_API_KEY       (for emotional vision)
#
# To set Supabase secrets, run:
#   supabase secrets set GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here
#   supabase secrets set LIVEKIT_API_KEY=your-key-here
#   supabase secrets set LIVEKIT_API_SECRET=your-secret-here
#   supabase secrets set OVERSHOOT_API_KEY=your-key-here
#
# See SETUP.md for detailed instructions.
